not pay interest on the deposited amount?

00:09:43.094 --> 00:09:44.444
A savings account.

00:09:44.685 --> 00:09:46.364
B. Fixed deposit account.

00:09:46.635 --> 00:09:49.994
C. Current account D,
recurring deposit account.

00:09:50.444 --> 00:09:52.729
Understand the question
before moving to explanation.

