savings, not business transactions.

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:22.640
Option C. Current account is specifically
for businesses, allows unlimited

00:10:22.640 --> 00:10:24.860
transactions and doesn't pay interest.

00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:26.270
It's a perfect match.

00:10:26.485 --> 00:10:30.255
